{"tid":2439981,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Zack Snyder版《正義聯盟》不小心在 HBO Max 上提前洩漏了","createTime":"2021-03-09T15:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T09:42:17.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"762e6ba7e54905520ccdb3e7507018ab9ba01fa9","tid":2439981,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/d348d420-8095-11eb-b6b6-b05418aa2c66\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2Fd348d420-8095-11eb-b6b6-b05418aa2c66&h=89549805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDC 超級英雄的粉絲們應該都知道，在 3 月 18 日史奈德剪輯版的《正義聯盟》將會在 HBO Max 正式上線。但讓人沒想到的是，在那之前 WarnerMedia 搞出了一個大烏龍。在距離影片開播還剩下不足十日的今天，正片中的相當一部分居然提前在 HBO Max 洩漏了...<br />\n<br />\n具體來說，早些時候一部分想在 HBO Max 上看《湯姆貓和傑利鼠》（Tom &amp; Jerry）的用戶，在點開影片後的等來的卻是以 4:3 比例播放的重剪版《正義聯盟》。後續 WarnerMedia 證實了此事，承認史奈德版確實「在 HBO Max 上短暫出現」，並表示自己「在發現後的幾分鐘內就修復了錯誤」。但即便如此，據說有些用戶仍看到了長達一個多小時的片段，這洩漏幅度也著實是不小了呢...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/hbo-max-leak-justice-league-snyder-cut-063048101.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fhbo-max-leak-justice-league-snyder-cut-063048101.html&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=95e193fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/hbo-max-leak-justice-league-snyder-cut-063048101.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c2d69f2761816f9ed662b55e8c761bfcc33a466","tid":2439981,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d48ca64da4ca4675e51017fb91d88b1fafdc48a","tid":2439981,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:47:55.000Z","msg":"同foxy d AV用假名有咩分別"},{"pid":"d0